#: org.kde.sweeper.desktop:142
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"Helps to clean unwanted traces the user leaves on the system and to regain "
"disk space removing unused temporary files"
msgstr ""
"Adjuta nettar tracias non volite que le usator abandona sur le systema e "
"obtene spatio de disco quando on remove files temporanee"
